b.Develop MFSCwebsite. Utilize social mediato sharefire-prevention information and resources. (Priority: High)'),
(4, 0, 2, 3, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 1, 0, 'Defensible Space regulations within Local Responsibility Areas', null, 2540, 'county-wide', 2, 2017, null, null, 'While regulations exist at both the state and county level concerning maintenance of defensible space and other fire safe issues, those regulations do not apply to Local Responsibility Areas where the local fire department is responsible for suppression of wild land fires.LRA regulations would assist with various fire safe issuesthat currently cannot be addressed or enforced.
Recommendations:
