(4, 0, 2, 3, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 1, 0, 'Fuel breaks around telecommunication and other sites important for emergency operations', null, 2540, 'county-wide', 2, 2017, null, null, 'There are many telecommunication sites throughout Modoc County that are important for emergency communication and need fuel breaks around them for protection.
