(4, 0, 2, 3, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 1, 0, 'Maintain Existing fuel breaks within Modoc County', null, 2540, 'county-wide', 2, 2017, null, null, 'MFSC and other partners have implemented many fuel breaks in Modoc County.Many of these need maintenance to maintain their effectiveness.As part of the ongoing efforts to ensure Modoc County communities continue to be protected and reduce risk from wild land fires, efforts should be made to monitor and evaluate the implementation and effectiveness of community fire safetyprojects.Those projects designed to create defensible space around community structures and individual residences should be monitored on an annual basis to reinforce implementation and to ensure they are properlyand effectively implemented.
