(4, 0, 2, 3, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 1, 0, 'Improve Coordination & Tracking', null, 2540, 'City of Santa Rosa area', 2, 2020, null, null, '1. Develop a robust GIS database of fuel treatments occurring on public and private lands in order to fully understand the extent of these exiting actions.At a minimum, the following categories should be used to track projects including project name, georeferenced data, date started, date completed, method of treatment, acres or feet completed, and total money spent.
